From 964a7d18f1f17a6ca70e1f3f2aeca767545d982a Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: GitHub Copilot <copilot@github.com>
Date: Thu, 26 Feb 2026 19:18:30 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Fix documentation inconsistencies in
 Generate-code-from-TypeSpec.md and Quickstart-on-how-to-write-tests.md

- Fix incorrect pnpm install command: `npm install -g @pnpm` -> `npm install -g pnpm`
  The package name on npm is `pnpm`, not `@pnpm`.
- Update Quickstart-on-how-to-write-tests.md examples to use vitest instead of mocha/chai:
  - Replace `import { assert } from "chai"` with vitest imports in both example files
  - Replace `import { Context } from "mocha"` with `import type { TestInfo } from "@azure-tools/test-recorder"`
  - Update `createRecorder` function signature to use `TestInfo` instead of mocha `Context`
  - Update `new Recorder(context.currentTest)` to `new Recorder(context)`
  - Update `beforeEach` callbacks to use vitest-style arrow functions with `ctx` parameter

Co-authored-by: Copilot <223556219+Copilot@users.noreply.github.com>
---
 documentation/Generate-code-from-TypeSpec.md  |  2 +-
 .../Quickstart-on-how-to-write-tests.md       | 21 +++++++++----------
 2 files changed, 11 insertions(+), 12 deletions(-)

diff --git a/documentation/Generate-code-from-TypeSpec.md b/documentation/Generate-code-from-TypeSpec.md
index 73df7f4e32..990b5ceef5 100644
--- a/documentation/Generate-code-from-TypeSpec.md
+++ b/documentation/Generate-code-from-TypeSpec.md
